<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-7984] @SelfType does not allow trait to be added dynamically</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-7984</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When trying to add dynamically a trait T with a SelfType type restriction on class C, to an instance of that class C, the script throws : &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;org.codehaus.groovy.runtime.typehandling.GroovyCastException: Cannot cast object &apos;C@92dae4&apos; with class &apos;C&apos; to class &apos;T&apos;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>windows 7, java 8, groovy script</environment>
